    public static class SynthesizePN.EventStateSeparationProblems

implements java.lang.Iterable<Pair<State,java.lang.String>>
    Iterable for iterating over all event/state separation problems of a transition system. An event/state separation problem consists of a state and an event that is not enabled in this state.
